OL,3,CPeople urged to 'use water wisely' as
OL,4,Criver levels drop across Wales
OL,6,FHeulyn Gwyn Davies, the company's Head
OL,7,Fof Strategic Communications urged
OL,8,Fpeople to "use the water you need, but
OL,9,Fuse it carefully."
OL,11,FHe said: "in the short term we are
OL,12,Fexpecting some rainfall over the next
OL,13,Fweek, what we believe and what we
OL,14,Funderstand is that it's not sustained
OL,15,For prolonged rainfall which was we
OL,16,Fwould need."
OL,18,FAround 95% of Wales' water comes from
OL,19,Freservoir storage or rivers with
OL,20,Fcurrent levels below what is expected
OL,21,Ffor this time of year.
