OL,3,CPeople urged to 'use water wisely' as
OL,4,Criver levels drop across Wales
OL,6,FProvisional statistics from the Met
OL,7,FOffice confirmed Wales saw 99.3mm of
OL,8,Frain this season, which is about a
OL,9,Fthird (36%) of the rain normally
OL,10,Fexpected throughout all of spring.
OL,12,FUsually, by this time of year, Wales
OL,13,Fwould have had 87% of its Spring rain.
OL,15,FDeputy First Minister Huw Irranca
OL,16,FDavies MS has said whilst people are
OL,17,Fenjoying the warm weather, it is
OL,18,Fsomething that needs to be taken
OL,19,Fseriously.
